                GOD</Bold></i><Bold>.�</Bold>�������� ( Ezk 29<Bold>:</Bold> 17-20 )</Paragraph>
        <Paragraph></Paragraph>
        <Paragraph>As we saw in the former passage<Bold>,</Bold> Nebuchadrezzar served a great service destroying
            Tyrus<Bold>,</Bold> and because of that<Bold>,</Bold> God awarded him the honor of becoming the
            conqueror of
            Egypt<Bold>.</Bold> Something similar happened to Jehu<Bold>.</Bold></Paragraph>
        <Paragraph></Paragraph>
        <Paragraph><Bold>�</Bold><i>Thus <Bold>Jehu destroyed Baal out of Israel.</Bold> Howbeit <Bold>from the sins
